token_info.name: Super Awesome Jampack
token_info.description: One of the first pieces of creative coding I remember seeing was "Jampack01" by Yugo Nakamura in 2004. Described as "motion logic with rigit body dynamics" on one of the few references I can still find online (https://thefwa.com/cases/yugop). This is my attempt to recreate it as best as I remember it to be. Build with a custom Box2D physics engine, and a custom audio generator.
